      <scopecontent id="aspace_9c2a69022821af8a0ba902e159cd34d6">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Bills, receipts, and miscellaneous papers of the Livingston household of Lawrence, Long Island. Included are reading lists for the Half Hour Reading Club. Principal family members are James LaRhett Livingston and his wife, Frances Park Forsyth Livingston.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
